wiki.summary: “KRZY TRAIN” marks Trippie Redd and Travis Scott’s first official reunion after 2017’s “Dark Knight Dummo.” The song contains an infectious guitar riff, paired with flexible vocals from Trippie — heard on songs like “PSYCHO” from MANSION MUSIK — and a laid-back mood from Travis Scott, gliding listeners through the track. It was first previewed in 2022, and once again on January 12, 2023, after Trippie teased him and Travis' second collaboration. On the snippet, the guitar solo intro was previewed in full. Read more on Last.fm.
